## 可用 MCP 工具

### `get_results(run_id: str, status_filter: str | None = None) → dict`

获取执行结果详情。`status_filter` 可选值：`pass`、`fail`、`error`、`skipped`。

**调用示例**：
```python
# 获取失败用例
get_results(run_id="20260609_143022_a3f1", status_filter="fail")

# 获取错误用例
get_results(run_id="20260609_143022_a3f1", status_filter="error")

# 获取全部结果
get_results(run_id="20260609_143022_a3f1")
```

**返回示例（失败用例）**：
```json
{
  "case_id": "TC-API-ORDERS-003",
  "run_id": "20260609_143022_a3f1",
  "env": "dev",
  "status": "fail",
  "duration_ms": 320,
  "request_snapshot": {
    "method": "POST",
    "url": "https://dev-api.example.com/api/orders",
    "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json", "Authorization": "Bearer ***"},
    "body": {"product_id": 999, "quantity": 1}
  },
  "response_snapshot": {
    "status_code": 500,
    "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"},
    "body": {"error": "Internal Server Error", "message": "Database connection timeout"},
    "duration_ms": 320
  },
  "assertions_result": [
    {"type": "status_code", "operator": "eq", "expected": 200, "actual": 500, "passed": false},
    {"type": "jsonpath", "path": "$.data.order_id", "operator": "type", "expected": "int", "actual": null, "passed": false}
  ],
  "error": null
}
```

**返回示例（错误用例）**：
```json
{
  "case_id": "TC-API-AUTH-010",
  "run_id": "20260609_143022_a3f1",
  "env": "dev",
  "status": "error",
  "duration_ms": 0,
  "request_snapshot": null,
  "response_snapshot": null,
  "assertions_result": [],
